name: Leopard Nidalee
description: Nidalee roams the tall grasses and bubbling tar pits of her home, a prehistoric savannah teeming with natural magic. She protects her leap of leopards by taking the appearance of their hunters, deceiving and disarming human threats with her wild skill.
